imdb.plot outline: Cupid's arrows strike young Chinese in search of true love in this energetic modernized dating show, set in romantic Thamestown, Shanghai. Fun-filled activities and flirtatious speed dating make every episode an adventure! Hosted by actress Wang Yinan.
imdb.title: My Cupid
